spring:
  mail:
    host: smtp.gmail.com
    port: 587
    username: <gmail-username>
    password: <gmail-password>
    properties:
      mail:
        smtp:
          auth: true
          starttls:
            enable: true


//////////////////
*********************
/////////////////

IMPORTANT -

This will NOT work if the 'Allow Less Secure App' feature is turned off for the sending account. Switch it ON here - https://myaccount.google.com/lesssecureapps